    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been well-loved and is in great shape. It runs super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. I've kept up with the basics, so it's all set for its new home. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that won't let you down. Come take it for a spin and see if it's the right fit for you!",
