    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, an engine celebrated for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock. The vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the integrity of the valvetrain and rotating assembly. The chassis retains its composure through Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and factory-spec bushings, offering a visceral analog driving experience with precise turn-in and exceptional high-speed stability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
