      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of well-maintained engineering and style. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, featuring premium upholstery that remains firm and comfortable, complemented by a fully operational climate control and sound system. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals, ensuring a responsive and dependable driving experience. With a solid service history, recent fluid changes, and tires with plenty of tread remaining, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance needs. It offers a refined ride that feels tight and composed, making it an ideal choice for someone who values both performance and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34500.0,
