    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s not fresh off the showroom floor, but it still looks great and drives like a dream! Perfect for someone who wants a quality car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
