      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb mechanical baseline for the purist. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine maintains excellent compression across all cylinders with the dual-VANOS system recently recalibrated for optimal variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp gate engagement, transferring torque through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and proactive reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure longitudinal rigidity. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining factory-spec kinematics and turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road-use patina, the drivetrain and chassis integrity remain the focal points of this well-maintained example.",
